  <summary date="2013-04-15T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Buffett Rule Act of 2013 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers to donate an amount (not less than $1), in addition to any tax owed, which shall be deposited in the general fund of the Treasury and transferred to an account used to reduce the public debt.&#160; Requires such donation to be designated on&#160;a taxpayer's income tax return at the time such return is filed.</summary>
